content:
Yes, some of these shops do have online shopping options or delivery services. Here are some that I found:

1. Melbournalia - offers online shopping on their website and ships internationally. 2. The National Gallery of Victoria Design Store - has an online store with delivery options available. 3. The Miniature Bookshop - offers online shopping on their website and ships internationally. 4. The Aboriginal Cultural Gifts - has an online store with shipping available within Australia. 5. The Big Design Market - has an online store with shipping available within Australia. However, it's always a good idea to check the individual shop's website or contact them directly to confirm their shipping policies and delivery options.
